title: Ep 17: 50 Shades of Grey & Foucault Guest is Me
description: This episode I ride solo, dawg. We cover 50 Shades of Grey and why my cousin loves it so much. Also, what does it have to do with Michel Foucault? TONS! Why was I going to S&M clubs as a teenager in LA? You'll have to listen to find out...
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
